<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Consumer Packaged Goods (CPG) | DGT</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            height: 80vh;
            background: url('/images/industryConsumerPkgGoods.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .hero-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            max-width: 600px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Main Container */
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        /* Sections */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Key Solutions Grid */
        .grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            flex: 1 1 calc(50% - 20px);
            min-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Technology Stack */
        .tools {
            background: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Call to Action */
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .cta a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .card {
                flex: 1 1 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Consumer Packaged Goods (CPG)</h1>
            <p>Revolutionizing consumer goods with AI-powered demand forecasting and personalized marketing.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About CPG -->
    <div class="container">
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Transforming the Consumer Goods Industry with AI</h2>
            <p>DGT leverages AI to help CPG companies optimize supply chains, personalize customer experiences, and drive efficiency. Our solutions enable brands to predict demand, enhance marketing strategies, and improve overall operational performance.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Key AI Solutions -->
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Key AI-Powered Solutions</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Demand Forecasting</h3>
                    <p>AI-driven sales prediction models to optimize inventory and reduce waste.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Personalized Marketing</h3>
                    <p>AI-powered customer segmentation and targeted campaigns for higher engagement.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>AI-Powered Supply Chain</h3>
                    <p>Real-time AI insights to streamline logistics, reduce costs, and improve efficiency.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Automated Retail Analytics</h3>
                    <p>AI-powered insights to track sales trends, consumer behavior, and market demand.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Tools & Technologies -->
        <section class="section tools">
            <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
            <p><strong>Salesforce Consumer Goods Cloud</strong> | AI Analytics | Power BI | Retail AI Solutions</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <section class="section cta">
            <h2>Drive Innovation in CPG with AI</h2>
            <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
